                  PLANNED CHANGES IN VERSION 0.3 

-- use of model$calculate() rather than (or in addition to) calculate(model)

-- nodeVectors as data structure for referring to collections of nodes as well as replacing nodeFunctionVectors

-- implementation of is.na(values(model, nodes))




                     CHANGES IN VERSION 0.2

-- Internal changes to decrease time to build models and nimbleFunctions.

-- Multivariate conjugate updaters now included in our MCMC implementation, as well as block updating on multivariate nodes.

Bug fixes

-- Fixed handling of NA and NaN.

-- Fixed issue with specifying multivariate nodes as rows/columns of matrices

-- Fixed an error in the conjugacy system

-- Fixed an issue with building the NIMBLE package for Windows.

